# Capstone Readiness - {{ report_title }}

This folder is the final local synthesis for the DevSecOps Cloud-Native lab around `{{ app.name }}`.

It aggregates the readiness modules generated by k8s-forge: Kubernetes raw, Helm, Ingress / TLS, Linkerd, NetworkPolicy, Kyverno, Supply Chain, CI GitHub Actions, GitOps ArgoCD, Observability, Logging, Tracing, Terraform, Ansible, and Security Audit readiness.

## What this dossier does

- Summarizes what was generated locally.
- Explains what is ready for review.
- Lists what remains manual.
- Lists runtime dependencies.
- Documents limits and out-of-scope areas.
- Prepares stabilization toward `v1.0.0 readiness`.

## What this dossier does not do

It does not deploy, scan, contact a cluster, contact a cloud provider, push Git changes, create sensitive values, or prove runtime compliance. It is a local Markdown synthesis, not a runtime validation report.
